{"tid":1537624,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"（多台）全民皆兵，義教防身方法及體能訓練正式上線","createTime":"2019-09-04T03:51:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-20T07:55:32.000Z","uid":115955,"like":30,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"a8a8111153edcc3792403e37409b053a09338714","tid":1537624,"uid":115955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T03:51:10.000Z","msg":"其實我由7月開始都有搞，不過嗰時就好低調咁搞，不過其實宜加啲狗都痴撚左線<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />人人都最少要識啲要練習過<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n主要係教大家有一個意識當有襲擊的時候。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我發現好多人都冇一個反應去準備應付一啲突如其來的事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，最少要有個概念要點預防，同如果真係畀人襲擊緊，應該點樣諗去走或保護自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n逢星期四<br />\n2000-2130<br />\n防身及體能<br />\n最多20人一班<br />\n跑馬地馬場<br />\n如果有興趣，可以留tg或者搵我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我重申<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我唔係教你地點樣去勇武，係教你點樣保護自己既概念<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一日未上警車一日都要嘗試走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />反正都畀狗打同告架啦，一定要拼命走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"435c14c0dda43074ab6aa7dd1feb31bd56a7b516","tid":1537624,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T03:51:32.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n [行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"07015c47573fb4b1e11397e6573ec17b9404a72e","tid":1537624,"uid":115955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T03:52:25.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"b8bb768d08ac7b557d493bade5e854a4d31ef1a5","tid":1537624,"uid":115955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T03:54:38.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"95a3178c0b316319cf1119f00b8fe092f6275fdd","tid":1537624,"uid":254358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T03:55:34.000Z","msg":"幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b09bdaa4af6914fe3e87dee9e2d3389c6d83f19f","tid":1537624,"uid":115579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T03:55:58.000Z","msg":"推<i